query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 1
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('c++14',
'db2',
'doctrine',
'imagemagick',
'ionic3',
'jquery-validate',
'jupyter-notebook',
'mingw',
'odata',
'operator-overloading',
'swift4',
'synchronization',
'type-conversion',
'user-controls',
'wpf-controls');
